Rating: 4
This is a KEEPER. Children loved it, no leftovers at all. I followed the recipe exactly. With 3 kids and 3 different activity schedules I made this ahead of time and put the chicken in a baking dish, then made the sauce which I poured over the chicken. I covered it with foil and reheated individual portions at 350 for 20 minutes. I made NearEast Rice Pilaf and fresh green beans. The rice reheats nicely in the microwave. This is GREAT to have on those busy nights when everyone is eating at different times!

