Rating: 3
This recipe was not only simple and quick to prepare, but surprisingly tasty. The reduction sauce was delicious and really packed a flavorful puch to what could have been just ho-hum sauteed chicken. I recommend doubling the garlic and reducing the worcestershire sauce to 1 tbls.

